Package: altermative
Version: 0.1.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: arm64
Depends: libwebkit2gtk-4.1-0, libgtk-3-0
Maintainer: Russell Haskell <rhask87062@gmail.com>
Description: GPU-accelerated terminal workspace with AI integration
 Altermative is a cross-platform terminal emulator built in Rust
 with tiling workspace, AI chat, embedded browser, and file preview.
